OL,3,CFears care home could close after 40
OL,4,Cyears due to NHS 'bed blocking'
OL,6,F"I would feel there's nothing now to
OL,7,Flook forward to or enjoy because this
OL,8,Fis definitely a one-off, isn't it.
OL,10,F"All the staff here are gorgeous and
OL,11,Fwe get lots of hugs and cuddles and if
OL,12,Fwe're upset we can have a little weep
OL,13,Fon their shoulder and if we're happy
OL,14,Fwe can have a little sing song."
OL,16,FElspeth was previously cared for by
OL,17,Fher daughter Penelope.
OL,19,FShe added: "A group of our most
OL,20,Fvulnerable people in society are being
OL,21,Fgiven a great disservice.
