OL,3,CFears care home could close after 40
OL,4,Cyears due to NHS 'bed blocking'
OL,6,F"It's a scandal. It really is.
OL,8,F"It's just not fair.
OL,10,F"This home has been running for almost
OL,11,F40 years, for most of them without any
OL,12,Fvacancies.
OL,14,F"Now, despite an ageing population,
OL,15,Fit's almost a quarter empty."
OL,17,FThe National Care Association says
OL,18,Fmany independent care homes are in a
OL,19,Fsimilar position.
