OL,3,CFears care home could close after 40
OL,4,Cyears due to NHS 'bed blocking'
OL,6,FNadra Ahmed from the organisation
OL,7,Fsaid: "From what we hear from
OL,8,Fproviders, they have got vacancies but
OL,9,Fthey're not being approached to take
OL,10,Fpeople out of their local hospitals
OL,11,Ffor discharge.
OL,13,F"I think the most important thing to
OL,14,Frealise is that the care homes need to
OL,15,Fbe running full in order to be viable
OL,16,Fbecause of the economic climate and we
OL,17,Falso know that the fees are quite
OL,18,Fwoefully inadequate in many ways for
OL,19,Fthe types of people we're looking
OL,20,Fafter.
