OL,6,F"We've also got a crisis in
OL,7,Femployment, so a care home, if it's
OL,8,Frunning a full complement of staff,
OL,9,Fits outgoings will be much greater if
OL,10,Fit hasn't got a full complement of
OL,11,Fresidents.
OL,13,F"It's not rocket science to realise
OL,14,Fthat will have an impact on that
OL,15,Fservice and they'll have to start
OL,16,Fthinking about actually knowing how
OL,17,Fmany beds they have open and reducing
OL,18,Ftheir workforce, which makes no sense
OL,19,Fwhen we know the NHS needs them and
OL,20,Factually people in the community may
OL,21,Fneed it as well."
