OL,6,FIn a statement, a Government
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We're taking
OL,8,Faction to ensure the health and care
OL,9,Fsystem works closely together to
OL,10,Ftackle delayed discharge, including
OL,11,Finvesting an additional #1 billion
OL,12,Fthis year to support the NHS and local
OL,13,Fauthorities to ensure timely and
OL,14,Feffective discharge from hospital."
